import React from 'react'
import Home from './Home'
import { Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

    return (
        <>

        <Route path="/" component={Home}/>

        <Route path="/" component={Home}/>
        <Route path="/" component={Home}/>
    
            </Switch>
        </>

}

export default App
